(31393, 396, 396, 6, 0, 0, 500, 500, 0, 'Hello, $c! We have been granted an audience with the White Tiger. The Vale of Eternal Blossoms was recently savaged by our Warchief, and we are arguing that both the Alliance and Horde should be permitted back inside to repair the damage.$b$bThe Vale is a sacred place. I believe my wife Leza saw it in a vision - it\'s what brought my people to Pandaria. We must save it!$b$bDo you think we will be allowed inside?', 63305), -- Temple of the White Tiger
(30515, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You did it! At the very least, we have justice, and safety, though in the process we have lost so much.\n\nRegardless, it has been decided. We will join the Horde, and with your help, rebuild this village.', 63305), -- Challenge Accepted
(30513, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well... we are alive, and that is better than we could have hoped for without your help.\n\nBut, if this is truly to become a base of operations for you, and if we are to join your Horde, there is one more thing you must do to guarantee our security.', 63305), -- Eastwind Rest
(30510, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Where have you been, $n? Nevermind. As you can see, we survived the battle at the Jade Serpent.$B$BUnfortunately, so did... they.', 63305), -- General Nazgrim has Awakened
(31255, 2, 1, 0, 0, 0, 500, 0, 0, 'Oh, you are a friend of Cho\'s? Welcome! Welcome!$b$bI would serve you a banquet, but as you can see, we are in dire straights at the moment.$b$bSay, would you be willing to lend us a hand?', 63305), -- The Road to Kun-Lai
(32108, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<This fire will signal the full might of the Horde invasion fleet to land on this beach, beginning Garrosh\'s campaign in Pandaria.>', 63305), -- Domination Point
(32250, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done. Our presence here will not be denied!', 63305), -- The Might of the Warchief
(32249, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You are just in time. The Warchief is about to land. Once this site passes his inspection, the fleet will follow.', 63305), -- Meet the Scout
(90879, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, I can smell the pretzels from here. Ye\'ve cooked up a spread that\'ll keep even the pickiest dwarves satisfied!', 63305), -- Brewmaster's Kitchen
