(32403, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Let\'s press on.', 63305), -- It Starts in the Sewers
(32402, 2, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good... you\'ve arrived. It\'s not a good day to be Horde in Dalaran.$b$bJaina\'s called for the exile of all the Sunreavers. You and I are going to save as many as we can - including Archmage Aethas Sunreaver himself - and then get out of here as fast as possible.', 63305), -- The Situation In Dalaran
(32328, 1, 1, 66, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You found the bell! And Fanlyr teleported it to Silvermoon for study, as instructed? The Horde will put this to good use.$b$bYou have done the Horde a great service today. Lok\'tar, friend!', 63305), -- Victorious Return
(32327, 66, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well executed, $r! I knew we could count on you.$b$bNow to get off this wretched tree.', 63305), -- The Darnassus Mission
(32326, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '$n! So glad Nazgrim selected you.$b$bIt\'s taken a great deal of the Horde\'s effort to get you here through Jaina\'s traps. Maintaining our illusion this close to Darnassus is considerably expensive.$b$bFurthermore, the Sunreavers of Dalaran are risking their neutrality by assisting the Horde with this operation.$b$bIn other words, we expect only the best from you.', 63305), -- Insertion
(32392, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Darnassus, is it?$B$BThe Alliance believes they have won the day. Now, when their arrogance is at its greatest, is our opportunity to pluck the prize from their fingers.', 63305), -- The Divine Bell
(32391, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Alliance beat us here. How could this happen?', 63305), -- The Ruins of Korune
(32368, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What did you see, $c?', 63305), -- Memory Wine
(32448, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, very good. This is the last thing we needed.', 63305), -- Ties with the Past
(32363, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Thank you for coming, $n.', 63305), -- The Kun-Lai Expedition
(32330, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This reckless use of my people by Garrosh is becoming intolerable. If you had not been here to assist I dread to think what might have happened.', 63305), -- What's in the Box?
(32329, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Warchief \"demands\" progress? His impatience is growing more destructive with each command.$b$bAs it stands, we could use your expertise.', 63305), -- Get My Results!
(32352, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You bested my defenders? Finally, one who can control $Ghis:her; hatred and violence!$B$BI need more $Gmen:women; like you.', 63305), -- A Gathering Storm
(32351, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well met, $c. You were sent from Domination Point? Very well. We have much to discuss.', 63305), -- Echoes of Thunder
(32384, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We managed to capture our quarry. \n\nIn truth, though, I am not sure what our next move should be. I will contact the leaders of our allies and see if they have ideas - I don\'t know that our arcane talents are going to pry the secrets of our mogu captive.', 63305), -- Trapping the Leader
(32379, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good. There\'s quite a bit to pore through here... \n\nI will have the Reliquary investigate these. Surely we can use them to discern more of the secrets of these Korune mogu.', 63305), -- Legacy of the Korune
(32378, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good. We should be ready to make our move.', 63305), -- Clearing a Path
(32376, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, good. You have come. \n\nAgain, I apologize for the cryptic note - but Garrosh is increasingly distrustful of us. I do not want this operation disturbed by hasty action on his part.', 63305), -- To the Valley!
(32192, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We blood elves have served the Horde faithfully. Lately, I wonder what we have to gain from Garrosh\'s leadership.', 63305), -- Bloodlines
(32244, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Yes, this is remarkable! This is just the kind of artifact that we came here to find!', 63305), -- The Korune
(32191, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah! Well done! With the guardians gone, we should be able to excavate these ruins safely.', 63305), -- Ancient Guardians
(32190, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well met, $c. We are an archaeological expedition, sent to excavate these ruins. We had no idea that this area was crawling with dangerous mogu.', 63305), -- To Mogujia
(32372, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The orcs have changed. My Horde has changed. Do I kill my fellow orcs until it is once again \"my\" Horde? Do I have any right to try force the Horde to be what it once was?$b$bThese are troubling times. But for now, I must see to Vol\'jin\'s people.', 63305), -- De-Subjugation
(32320, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Vol\'jin has saved my life many times in the past. To see my own Kor\'kron used against his people cuts deeper than I can put into words.', 63305), -- The Horde Is Family
(32319, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Thrall stares at the stone you have handed him.>$b$bVol\'jin\'s hearthstone? My friend, has it come to this?', 63305), -- Find Thrall!
(32318, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Very good. These should work nicely.', 63305), -- Regeneration Takes Time
(32284, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah! You received my note. Very good. Vol\'jin is near death, and I will need your help healing his wounds.', 63305), -- Someone You Should See
(32257, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hmm... very interesting. This tablet will yield many secrets, indeed.', 63305), -- Voice of the Gods
(32242, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Warchief sent you? What does he say?', 63305), -- Buried Secrets
(32256, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What do you have to report?', 63305), -- Rise Of An Empire
(29397, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aww, it\'s just a stein voucher... Maybe you\'re just playing hard to get.  So here\'s this year\'s stein for you.$b$bBut I suspect I\'ll be seeing a lot more of you.  After all, if you want any Brewfest tokens redeemed, I\'m your girl...$b$bOr maybe I\'m his girl...  $b$bOooohhh... or his...', 63305), -- A New Supplier of Souvenirs
(56764, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well eaten! Every time you win, you\'ll receive a token as a reward. Once you collect five, come back to me and I can award you with a beautiful trophy!', 63305), -- Brewfest Chowdown
(90870, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, ye\'ve done it! The cooks will be pleased.', 63305), -- Gathering the Grub
(84308, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Donate to taverns across Khaz Algar to cover the tab!', 63305), -- Bar Tab Barrel
