(80311, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, another student of the skies. Welcome to the Arboretum.', 63305), -- Order of the Cloud Serpent
(30015, 1, 404, 1, 0, 0, 500, 500, 0, 'Greetings, $n!$b$bWelcome to Dawn\'s Blossom, a home of my people.$b$bSadly I must depart. Alas, a Lorewalker\'s work is never done.$b$bMake yourself at home. Our people could surely make use of one with your talents.', 63305), -- Dawn's Blossom
(29967, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I\'d say repelling the attack is an understatement!', 63305), -- Boom Goes the Doonamite!
(29966, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Alliance must be purged from this land, $n!$b$bNo half-measures will do!', 63305), -- Burning Down the House
(29968, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, the smell of progress, and methane. ', 63305), -- Green-ish Energy
(29943, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Yes!$b$bBy Thrall\'s bloodied fist, I\'ve missed hunting Alliance!', 63305), -- Guerrillas in our Midst
(29824, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The most important thing we learned was that... not only have the Alliance befriended the jinyu, but they\'re giving them weapons, and teaching them how to use them.$b$bThe Alliance now control a force that outnumbers us thirty-to-one. And we - the HORDE - have befriended monkeys.', 63305), -- Scouting Report: Like Jinyu in a Barrel
(29823, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Yeah, I ran away. So blikkin\' what? If it weren\'t for me, Kiryn would be dead. Oh, wait... she\'s already dead... already...$b$bGo away! Riko\'s head hurts.', 63305), -- Scouting Report: The Friend of My Enemy
(29731, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'And that\'s how we found our Alliance captive.$b$bBut that\'s not all that happened. Not by a long shot...', 63305), -- Scouting Report: On the Right Track
(29730, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'So, as you can see, none of this is Riko\'s fault.', 63305), -- Scouting Report: Hostile Natives
(29971, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We may have a problem.', 63305), -- The Scouts Return
(29939, 479, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We\'ve just revolutionized how these cretins.. err, hozen, feed themselves.$b$bThey\'ll never be the same!', 63305), -- Boom Bait
(29942, 4, 1, 66, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Now everybody got grub! Great hozen wisdom in Eekle Eekle.$b$bMaybe Eekle Eekle become Chieftain someday...', 63305), -- Silly Wikket, Slickies are for Hozen
(29937, 11, 1, 94, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Yeah!$b$bNow that\'s the stuff. Just you wait and see...', 63305), -- Furious Fowl
(31239, 71, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ha ha! Wikket Grooked ookin\' Jinyu!', 63305), -- What's in a Name Name?
(29941, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good work $n.$b$bThe away team you assembled has departed.$b$bI hope Gorrok had the sense to change out of that ragged red shirt. I admire his patriotism, but he\'s had it on since we left Orgrimmar.$b$bThey won\'t be surprising anyone if he\'s wearing it...', 63305), -- Beyond the Horizon
(29936, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Impressive work, $n.$b$bIt had not occurred to me that we might somehow befriend these creatures.$b$bWith their acceptance, we can now turn our attention to more important matters.', 63305), -- Instant Messaging
(31241, 71, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wikket grookin\' makin\' hozen rich with shinies!$b$b$n makin\' a good second impression. And for hozen, number two is most important!', 63305), -- Wicked Wikkets
(31261, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ookin\' grookin, wikket!', 63305), -- Captain Jack's Dead
(29933, 4, 1, 94, 0, 0, 500, 0, 0, 'Woot! Woot! Wikket da Ook Dook!', 63305), -- The Bees' Knees
(29935, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hmm.$b$bMean wikkets fighting with nice wikkets?$b$bHozen fight mean wikkets too!', 63305), -- Orders are Orders
(29924, 4, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The dreaded Kher Shan is dead. You have avenged  Ick Ick, Nab Nab, Eet Eet, Bitty Bitty, and the others that Nibi Nibi couldn\'t remember.', 63305), -- Kill Kher Shan
(29879, 6, 273, 0, 0, 0, 500, 0, 0, 'Wikket save hozen? And bring slickies?$b$bHmm, maybe wikket not so bad.$b$bTooki Tooki never liked Dook Ookem anyway...', 63305), -- Swallowed Whole
(31167, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Not so different, you and I.$b$bI believe we can become good friends.', 63305), -- Family Tree
(31152, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am most grateful for the knowledge my forebears have passed on to me.$b$bI stand upon their shoulders.', 63305), -- Peering Into the Past
(31134, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'That is enough translating for one day, I think.$b$bThis experience has been an enlightening one, I hope.', 63305), -- If These Stones Could Speak
(31132, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I suppose the best way to explain what a Lorewalker is all about is to show you...', 63305), -- A Mile in My Shoes
(31121, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I will help you, traveler, but first I would like to learn a little about this Horde of yours...', 63305), -- Stay a While, and Listen
(29822, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Welcome, traveler.$b$bPlease, make yourself comfortable.', 63305), -- Lay of the Land
(29827, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Excellent! What a creative solution!$b$bThat should hold them off for a while.', 63305), -- Acid Rain
(29815, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh, yes, $n. This will do nicely.', 63305), -- Forensic Science
(31112, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Look at that!$b$bThese supplies should keep us kickin\' for a few more days.$b$bAnd my boots! Ya managed not to blow \'em up. Way ta go, $n!', 63305), -- They're So Thorny!
(29821, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This crate should be full of supplies...', 63305), -- Missed Me By... That Much!
(31999, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We may have won the battle against the Alliance, but we won\'t get any further with this many jabbering monkeys on our perimeter.$b$bThe hozen are our next target.', 63305), -- Nazgrim's Command
(31779, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The Alliance have been routed. You, Nazgrim, Kiryn, Gorrok, Shokia, and Rivett need a base of operations.$b$bThese flags will have to be changed.$b$bFor the Horde!', 63305), -- The Darkness Within
(31777, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I hope those ding-dongs enjoyed the party you threw for them!', 63305), -- Choppertunity
(31776, 66, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Blood and thunder, $n. Blood and thunder.', 63305), -- Strongarm Tactics
(31775, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The best thing about killing Alliance in Pandaria? It\'ll be months before they get any reinforcements.$b$bThis land will belong to the Horde, $c. We\'re nearly finished.', 63305), -- Assault on the Airstrip
(31778, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Although I can\'t understand why you chose to bring your war to our land, I can clearly see which side is more virtuous.$b$bThank you for your aid, $r.', 63305), -- Unreliable Allies
(29804, 6, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Zin\'jun is lost?$b$bThis is a dark day indeed, $gbrother:sister;. These vermin will pay!', 63305), -- Seein' Red
(29743, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'As you look over your sketch, you can\'t help but hope that these creatures don\'t really exist.', 63305), -- Monstrosity
(29765, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Zin\'Jun sobs...you think.>$b$bDey done killed Snuff...$b$bWhat\'d \'ol Snuff ever do ta dem? ', 63305), -- Cryin' My Eyes Out
(31774, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Zin\'Jun is grievously wounded, but senses that you\'re friendly.>$b$bMonkey-tings! Everywhere dere be dese monkey-tings!', 63305), -- Seeking Zin'jun
(31772, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well, it\'s not as much as I would have hoped, but it will have to do. I guess there is no sense in cryin\' over spilled brew.', 63305), -- Priorities!
(31773, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, so your conflict at the ruins is beginning to pollute the local wildlife? This is very troubling - I have never seen a reaction so intense.$b$bThank you for protecting the village, but it is a tragedy that those poor animals had to die.', 63305), -- Prowler Problems
(31771, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am glad you took responsibility for your actions. Left unchecked, negative emotions can quickly overwhelm an individual here, just as they started to overwhelm the one you call \"Nazgrim.\"', 63305), -- Face to Face With Consequence
(29694, 6, 274, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'These are the only survivors, $n?$b$bSo be it. We will play the hand fate has dealt us.$b$b<Gorrok lifts his head up high.>$b$bNumbers be damned. This is where heroes are made.', 63305), -- Regroup!
(31770, 5, 274, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Your fighting has brought about much destruction for our tiny village!$b$bWe have no interest in your war, but we will not turn your injured away.', 63305), -- You're Either With Us Or...
(31769, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 500, 0, 0, 'An air base - they had a hidden airbase here this entire time! Had I known I would\'ve kept more men on the guns, I would\'ve - Uaaghh -$b$b<The color drains from Nazgrim\'s face, and his body begins to exude a mysterious dark energy.>', 63305), -- The Final Blow!
(31768, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Haha! Good work, $n.$b$bLeave \'em nothing!', 63305), -- Fire Is Always the Answer
(31767, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good work, $c! We have them on their heels!', 63305), -- Finish Them!
(82356, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Task completed. The Council rewards you for assisting with earthen reunification.', 63163); -- A Large Bundle of Goods

