(4487, 'By order of King Wrynn, this land is to be scoured in all haste until the White Pawn is found and returned to safety.$b$bNo expense is to be spared in this effort, including - if necessary - the blood of any subjects who find themselves serving in this foreign land.$b$bThe families of any such heroes lost in this noble endeavor will be well cared for, and the one who secures the asset may name his reward.', 0, 0, 0, 63305); -- 4487

